Snippet: R W Apple Jr article on the prospects for America retaining its global power into the new century; maps (M)
LeadParagraph: IT was Henry Luce, as every red-blooded Yankee knows, who christened the 20th the American Century. He proved to be right, but that was not necessarily obvious throughout the 100 years.
